{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b509e540008b4c4d906ba75c73d6\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-06 10:04 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"4f2b817a","parentId":"471b4505","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:04:32.673Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"5ef5055e","parentId":"4f2b817a","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:04:43.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HALEI 在问关于长期记忆存储的问题。当前 OpenClaw 版本有内置的记忆系统（MEMORY.md + sqlite-vec 向量索引），他在考虑是否还需要安装第三方存储如 LanceDB、Mem0 这类。\n\n让我先了解一下当前 OpenClaw 内置存储的能力和价格情况，再给出建议。\n\n根据 MEMORY.md 中的记忆系统架构：\n- **memory-core**（OpenClaw 内置核心）\n- **sqlite-vec**（内置本地向量索引）\n- **MEMORY.md + daily.md**（长期文件记忆）\n- **.dreams/** — 向量语料存储\n\n所以 OpenClaw 已经有内置的向量存储能力了。\n\nHALEI 问的是\"就当前版本的存储价格\"，我需要了解一下：\n1. 当前 OpenClaw 内置存储的能力边界\n2. 第三方工具（如 LanceDB、Mem0）的优势在哪里\n3. 性价比对比\n\n\n4. 是否真的需要\n\n我应该查一下当前存储配置和内置能力，然后给出具体的建议。","thinkingSignature":"1602b52b9f900b18b3de02656c7ee63b547841c22e5900244c9c3ed0e9516a57"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题。让我先看一下当前 OpenClaw 内置存储的能力边界。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p1v1oqp44d4z_1","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.schema.lookup","path":"memory"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p1v1oqp44d4z_2","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"OpenClaw memory storage configuration vector sqlite-vec","corpus":"wiki"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":304,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":22287,"totalTokens":22748,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778033072673,"responseId":"0649d4b1433880572bc092509e4130a5"}}
