{"type":"message","id":"378a0a2a","parentId":"609cff12","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:14:33.025Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8acaeb47e74141548a7c630a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Mem0 ===\nmem0ai/mem0 | ⭐54844 | Universal memory layer for AI Agents\n  https://github.com/mem0ai/mem0\n\nsachitrafa/YourMemory | ⭐210 | Agentic AI memory with Ebbinghaus forgetting curve decay. +16pp better recall than Mem0 on LoCoMo.\n  https://github.com/sachitrafa/YourMemory\n\nMemTensor/HaluMem | ⭐129 | HaluMem is the first operation level hallucination evaluation benchmark tailored to agent memory systems.\n  https://github.com/MemTensor/HaluMem\n\npinkpixel-dev/mem0-mcp | ⭐93 | ✨ mem0 MCP Server: A memory system using mem0 for AI applications with model context protocl (MCP) integration. Enables long-term memory for AI agents as a drop-in MCP server.\n  https://github.com/pinkpixel-dev/mem0-mcp\n\nAIAnytime/Agent-Memory-Playground | ⭐37 | Agent Memory Playground: AI Agent Memory Design & Optimization Techniques\n  https://github.com/AIAnytime/Agent-Memory-Playground"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1177,"aggregated":"=== Mem0 ===\nmem0ai/mem0 | ⭐54844 | Universal memory layer for AI Agents\n  https://github.com/mem0ai/mem0\n\nsachitrafa/YourMemory | ⭐210 | Agentic AI memory with Ebbinghaus forgetting curve decay. +16pp better recall than Mem0 on LoCoMo.\n  https://github.com/sachitrafa/YourMemory\n\nMemTensor/HaluMem | ⭐129 | HaluMem is the first operation level hallucination evaluation benchmark tailored to agent memory systems.\n  https://github.com/MemTensor/HaluMem\n\npinkpixel-dev/mem0-mcp | ⭐93 | ✨ mem0 MCP Server: A memory system using mem0 for AI applications with model context protocl (MCP) integration. Enables long-term memory for AI agents as a drop-in MCP server.\n  https://github.com/pinkpixel-dev/mem0-mcp\n\nAIAnytime/Agent-Memory-Playground | ⭐37 | Agent Memory Playground: AI Agent Memory Desi