{"type":"message","id":"97f36d5a","parentId":"6d482fe9","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:33:40.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to search more widely on the web for a comprehensive evaluation. My previous searches via GitHub API and web_fetch were partially successful but limited. Let me now compile all the data I have and give a comprehensive comparison, since I do have substantial data already. Let me also check the OpenClaw docs for memory-lancedb and try to get more pricing info on Mem0 Cloud.\n\nLet me also check what the openclaw docs say about memory-lancedb and other memory options.","thinkingSignature":"9271f36a0cbc738c1e24e11409c596079331011eb2b78709678ad9f747a450e9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我已经有足够数据做完整评估了。让我先把之前的进程关掉，然后整理输出。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a108aae0fe5346c1883884ab","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"amber-claw"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b87b058e164d488fbdb7ed22","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"calm-cloud"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9363,"output":191,"cacheRead":33472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43026,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778034816340,"responseId":"0649db81bf89ae411e2a13862ffeba54"}}
