{"type":"message","id":"34bacbf5","parentId":"305f7345","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:45:19.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to understand the division of responsibilities between OpenViking and LanceDB in the \"OpenViking + LanceDB local\" self-hosted pattern. Let me explain clearly.\n\nFrom what I know:\n- **OpenViking** is the context database that manages memories, resources, and skills for agents - it has the filesystem paradigm, L0/L1/L2 layers, agent memory extraction, etc.\n- **LanceDB** is the underlying vector database that does the actual vector storage and retrieval\n\nSo OpenViking sits on top of LanceDB (or can use it as a backend). OpenViking handles the semantic organization, the file system abstraction, memory categories, etc. \n\nLanceDB handles the actual vector storage and similarity search. When OpenViking stores memories, it generates embeddings through its own pipeline and then persists them through LanceDB's vector storage layer.","thinkingSignature":"32b9a1ba355845e289c9ab1e1712696234a11c5364994981baa578471df11b5b"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题。两者是**上下层关系**，不是二选一：\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────┐\n│         OpenViking              │  ← 上层：Agent 记忆抽象\n│  (文件系统语义、L0/L1/L2、       │\n│   Memory/Resource/Skill 分类、   │\n│   自动提取、自演进)              │\n└──────────────┬──────────────────┘\n               │  调用向量能力\n               ↓\n┌─────────────────────────────────┐\n│          LanceDB                │  ← 底层：向量存储引擎\n│  (向量索引、相似性搜索、          │\n│   多模态支持、TB级存储)           │\n└─────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 各自分工\n\n| | OpenViking | LanceDB |\n|--|-----------|---------|\n| **角色** | 记忆管理器 + Agent 接口 | 向量数据库引擎 |\n| **负责** | 记忆结构（Resource/Memory/Skill）<br>L0/L1/L2 分层<br>自动从对话提取记忆<br>记忆分类、检索逻辑<br>多 Agent 共享语义 | 原始向量存储<br>相似性搜索<br>多模态数据（图片/视频）<br>TB级数据规模 |\n| **类比** | 图书馆管理员（知道书在哪、怎么组织） | 图书馆书架（真正存放书的地方）|\n\n---\n\n## 简单说\n\n- **OpenViking** = 你的 AI 团队的大脑皮层（会思考、会分类、会提炼）\n- **LanceDB** = 你的 AI 团队的海马体（负责存储、调取记忆碎片）\n\n---\n\n**实际部署时**：OpenViking 内置了对 LanceDB 的支持，装好之后配置一下就能联动，不用自己写桥接代码。\n\n你们是倾向于**现在就在测试环境搭一套试试**，还是先确认清楚方案再动？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":568,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":53956,"totalTokens":54681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778035496370,"responseId":"0649de29d0e33140c02d287e98d00f4d"}}
