{"type":"message","id":"10883fe5","parentId":"9d80c13a","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:47:26.672Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking the same question again. I already answered this in the previous turn. I should give the same concise answer since the question is identical.","thinkingSignature":"bbafa730bd029a972ea87ca1ca3019c6f6a40914c0be44738851ef2ff8f6bc0c"},{"type":"text","text":"刚回答过，同样的问题——\n\n**OpenViking** = 大脑皮层（组织、提炼、分类记忆）\n**LanceDB** = 海马体（向量存储、相似性搜索）\n\n两者是上下层，OpenViking 内置支持 LanceDB，装好直接联动。\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 要不要现在在测试环境搭一套试试？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":109,"cacheRead":53731,"cacheWrite":691,"totalTokens":54688,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778035640973,"responseId":"0649deb92ac2f5ef4ecb19639b1570d6"}}
