{"type":"message","id":"f1d50f95","parentId":"4740d0bc","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:48:06.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HALEI is asking whether OpenViking + LanceDB integrates with their existing OpenClaw architecture. Yes, that's exactly the point - OpenViking was designed specifically for OpenClaw. Let me clarify this integration.","thinkingSignature":"0db6a096ef6d2a45af3ebed1225bf6dc5a6c8f0a8142531706e378b347a998fd"},{"type":"text","text":"对，**OpenViking 就是为 OpenClaw 设计的**。\n\n你现在的架构：\n```\nOpenClaw (多 Agent)\n├── main Agent（你）\n└── tts Agent（选品）\n    ↕\n内置 memory-core + sqlite-vec\n```\n\n加上 OpenViking + LanceDB 之后：\n```\nOpenClaw (多 Agent)\n├── main Agent\n└── tts Agent\n    ↕\nOpenViking（记忆抽象层）\n    ↕\nLanceDB（向量存储）\n```\n\n**不是替换，是叠加**——它们填补了多 Agent 共享知识库这个空白。\n\n你现在有的 memory-core 处理的是\"每个 Agent 自己的记忆\"，OpenViking 处理的是\"团队共享知识库\"，两个是不同维度的东西，可以共存。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":206,"cacheRead":54194,"cacheWrite":368,"totalTokens":54925,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778035677642,"responseId":"0649dede97ac94acc4faf98f40692481"}}
