{"type":"message","id":"7bd084b2","parentId":"fbc48fc2","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:54:14.867Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wz0icqmt8nwr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"63: | **Hybrid Retrieval** | Vector + BM25 full-text search, fused with cross-encoder reranking |\n65: | **Multi-Scope Isolation** | Per-agent, per-user, per-project memory boundaries |\n206: 3. Use Jina for reranker\n212: 9. retrieval mode=hybrid, vectorWeight=0.7, bm25Weight=0.3\n213: 10. rerank=cross-encoder, candidatePoolSize=12, minScore=0.6, hardMinScore=0.62\n254: Install this skill and your AI agent (Claude Code or OpenClaw) gains deep knowledge of every feature in memory-lancedb-pro. Just say **\"help me enable the best config\"** and get:\n257:   - Full Power (Jina + OpenAI) / Budget (free SiliconFlow reranker) / Simple (OpenAI only) / Fully Local (Ollama, zero API cost)\n275: > Full walkthrough: installation, configuration, and hybrid retrieval internals.\n319: | `src/store.ts` | LanceDB storage layer. Table creation / FTS indexing / Vector search / BM25 search / CRUD |\n321: | `src/retriever.ts` | Hybrid retrieval engine. Vector + BM25 → Hybrid Fusion → Rerank → Lifecycle Decay → Filter |\n322: | `src/scopes.ts` | Multi-scope access control |\n335: ## Core Features\n337: ### Hybrid Retrieval\n341:                        ├─→ Hybrid Fusion → Rerank → Lifecycle Decay Boost → Length Norm → Filter\n342: Query → BM25 FTS ─────┘\n346: - **BM25 Full-Text Search** — exact keyword matching via LanceDB FTS index\n347: - **Hybrid Fusion** — vector score as base, BM25 hits receive a weighted boost (not standard RRF — tuned for real-world recall quality)\n348: - **Configurable Weights** — `vectorWeight`, `bm25Weight`, `minScore`\n350: ### Cross-Encoder Reranking\n354: - Hybrid scoring: 60% cross-encoder + 40% original fused score\n357: ### Multi-Stage Scoring Pipeline\n361: | **Hybrid Fusion** | Combines semantic and exact-match recall |\n362: | **Cross-Encoder Rerank** | Promotes semantically precise hits |\n382: ### Multi-Scope Isolation\n400: - CJK-aware thresholds (Chinese: 6 chars vs English: 15 chars)\n405: <summary><strong>Compared to Built-in <code>memory-lancedb</code> (click to expand)</strong></summary>\n407: | Feature | Built-in `memory-lancedb` | **memory-lancedb-pro** |\n410: | BM25 full-text search | - | Yes |\n411: | Hybrid fusion (Vector + BM25) | - | Yes |\n412: | Cross-encoder rerank (multi-provider) | - | Yes |\n416: | Multi-scope isolation | - | Yes |\n450:     \"mode\": \"hybrid\",\n452:     \"bm25Weight\": 0.3,\n454:     \"rerank\": \"cross-encoder\",\n455:     \"rerankApiKey\": \"${JINA_API_KEY}\",\n456:     \"rerankModel\": \"jina-reranker-v3\",\n457:     \"rerankEndpoint\": \"https://api.jina.ai/v1/rerank\",\n458:     \"rerankProvider\": \"jina\",\n467:     \"maxHalfLifeMultiplier\": 3\n514: <summary><strong>Rerank Providers</strong></summary>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":890,"aggregated":"63: | **Hybrid Retrieval** | Vector + BM25 full-text search, fused with cross-encoder reranking |\n65: | **Multi-Scope Isolation** | Per-agent, per-user, per-project memory boundaries |\n206: 3. Use Jina for reranker\n212: 9. retrieval mode=hybrid, vectorWeight=0.7, bm25Weight=0.3\n213: 10. rerank=cross-encoder, candidatePoolSize=12, minScore=0.6, hardMinScore=0.62\n254: Install this skill and your AI agent (Claude Code or OpenClaw) gains deep knowledge of every feature in memory-lancedb-pro. Just say **\"help me enable the best config\"** and get:\n257:   - Full Power (Jina + OpenAI) / Budget (free SiliconFlow reranker) / Simple (OpenAI only) / Fully Local (Ollama, zero API cost)\n275: > Full walkthrough: installation, configuration, and hybrid retrieval internals.\n319: | `src/store.ts` | LanceDB storage layer. Table creation / FTS indexing / Vector search / BM25 search / CRUD |\n321: | `src/retriever.ts` | Hybrid retrieval engine. Vector + BM25 → Hybrid Fusion → Rerank → Lifecycle Decay → Filter |\n322: | `src/scopes.ts` | Multi-scope access control |\n335: ## Core Features\n337: ### Hybrid Retrieval\n341:                        ├─→ Hybrid Fusion → Rerank → Lifecycle Decay Boost → Length Norm → Filter\n342: Query → BM25 FTS ─────┘\n346: - **BM25 Full-Text Search** — exact keyword matching via LanceDB FTS index\n347: - **Hybrid Fusion** — vector score as base, BM25 hits receive a weighted boost (not standard RRF — tuned for real-world recall quality)\n348: - **Configurable Weights** — `vectorWeight`, `bm25Weight`, `minScore`\n350: ### Cross-Encoder Reranking\n354: - Hybrid scoring: 60% cross-encoder + 40% original fused score\n357: ### Multi-Stage Scoring Pipeline\n361: | **Hybrid Fusion** | Combines semantic and exact-match recall |\n362: | **Cross-Encoder Rerank** | Promotes semantically precise hits |\n382: ### Multi-Scope Isolation\n400: - CJK-aware thresholds (Chinese: 6 chars vs English: 15 chars)\n405: <summary><strong>Compared to Built-in <code>memory-lancedb</code> (click to expand)</strong></summary>\n407: | Feature | Built-in `memory-lancedb` | **memory-lancedb-pro** |\n410: | BM25 full-text search | - | Yes |\n411: | Hybrid fusion (Vector + BM25) | - | Yes |\n412: | Cross-encoder rerank (multi-provider) | - | Yes |\n416: | Multi-scope isolation | - | Yes |\n450:     \"mode\": \"hybrid\",\n452:     \"bm25Weight\": 0.3,\n454:     \"rerank\": \"cross-encoder\",\n455:     \"rerankApiKey\": \"${JINA_API_KEY}\",\n456:     \"rerankModel\": \"jina-reranker-v3\",\n457:     \"rerankEndpoint\": \"https://api.jina.ai/v1/rerank\",\n458:     \"rerankProvider\": \"jina\",\n467:     \"maxHalfLifeMultiplier\": 3\n514: <summary><strong>Rerank Providers</strong></summary>","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778036054866}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f24000f","parentId":"7bd084b2","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:54:14.867Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wz0icqmt8nwr_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 🧠 memory-lancedb-pro · OpenClaw Plugin\n\n**Enhanced Long-Term Memory Plugin for [OpenClaw](https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw)**\n\nHybrid Retrieval (Vector + BM25) · Cross-Encoder Rerank · Multi-Scope Isolation · Management CLI\n\n--\n[![LanceDB](https://img.shields.io/badge/LanceDB-Vectorstore-orange)](https://lancedb.com)\n[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)\n\n**English** | [简体中文](README_CN.md)\n\n</div>\n--\nThe built-in `memory-lancedb` plugin in OpenClaw provides basic vector search. **memory-lancedb-pro** takes it much further:\n\n| Feature | Built-in `memory-lancedb` | **memory-lancedb-pro** |\n|---------|--------------------------|----------------------|\n| Vector search | ✅ | ✅ |\n| BM25 full-text search | ❌ | ✅ |\n| Hybrid fusion (Vector + BM25) | ❌ | ✅ |\n| Cross-encoder rerank (Jina / custom endpoint) | ❌ | ✅ |\n--\n| `package.json` | NPM package info. Depends on `@lancedb/lancedb`, `openai`, `@sinclair/typebox` |\n| `cli.ts` | CLI commands: `memory list/search/stats/delete/delete-bulk/export/import/reembed/migrate` |\n| `src/store.ts` | LanceDB storage layer. Table creation / FTS indexing / Vector search / BM25 search / CRUD / bulk delete / stats |\n| `src/embedder.ts` | Embedding abstraction. Compatible with any OpenAI-API provider (OpenAI, Gemini, Jina, Ollama, etc.). Supports task-aware embedding (`taskQuery`/`taskPassage`) |\n| `src/retriever.ts` | Hybrid retrieval engine. Vector + BM25 → RRF fusion → rerank → recency / importance / length / decay weighting → noise filter → coarse MMR diversity. |\n| `src/recall-engine.ts` | Shared recall helpers: prompt gating, session repeated-injection suppression, tagged-block assembly, max-age filtering, and recent-per-key capping |\n| `src/auto-recall-final-selection.ts` | Generic auto-recall adapter. Maps `RetrievalResult` rows into final-selection candidates and applies generic `mmr | setwise-v2` behavior at the final cutoff seam |\n| `src/final-topk-setwise-selection.ts` | Shared final top-k selector. Owns shortlist presort, deterministic set-wise selection, lexical-overlap suppression, and optional embedding-based semantic redundancy suppression |\n--\n| `src/migrate.ts` | Migration tool. Migrates data from the built-in `memory-lancedb` plugin to Pro |\n\n---\n\n## Core Features\n\n### 1. Hybrid Retrieval\n\n```\nQuery → embedQuery() ─┐\n--\n- **Vector Search**: Semantic similarity via LanceDB ANN (cosine distance)\n- **BM25 Full-Text Search**: Exact keyword matching via LanceDB FTS index\n- **Fusion Strategy**: Vector score as base, BM25 hits get a 15% boost (tuned beyond traditional RRF)\n- **Configurable Weights**: `vectorWeight`, `bm25Weight`, `minScore`\n\n### 2. Cross-Encoder Reranking\n\n--\n- **Hybrid Scoring**: 60% cross-encoder score + 40% original fused score\n- **Graceful Degradation**: Falls back to cosine similarity reranking on API failure\n\n### 3. Multi-Stage Scoring Pipeline\n\n| Stage | Formula | Effect |\n--\n- CJK-aware thresholds (Chinese: 6 chars vs English: 15 chars)\n\n### 6. Noise Filtering\n\nFilters out low-quality content at both auto-capture and tool-store stages:\n- Agent refusal responses (\"I don't have any information\")\n--\n- `memoryReflection.enabled`: turn reflection features on/off\n- `memoryReflection.injectMode`:\n  - `inheritance-only` = inject inherited rules only\n  - `inheritance+derived` = inherited rules + derived-focus note on `/new` / `/reset`\n- `memoryReflection.recall.mode`:\n  - `fixed` = compatibility path\n--\n- `memoryReflection.storeToLanceDB`: store reflection event/item rows in LanceDB\n- `memoryReflection.agentId` (optional): use a dedicated reflection agent\n\nRecommended starter config:\n\n```json\n--\n    \"storeToLanceDB\": true,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":873,"aggregated":"# 🧠 memory-lancedb-pro · OpenClaw Plugin\n\n**Enhanced Long-Term Memory Plugin for [OpenClaw](https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw)**\n\nHybrid Retrieval (Vector + BM25) · Cross-Encoder Rerank · Multi-Scope Isolation · Management CLI\n\n--\n[![LanceDB](https://img.shields.io/badge/LanceDB-Vectorstore-orange)](https://lancedb.com)\n[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)\n\n**English** | [简体中文](README_CN.md)\n\n</div>\n--\nThe built-in `memory-lancedb` plugin in OpenClaw provides basic vector search. **memory-lancedb-pro** takes it much further:\n\n| Feature | Built-in `memory-lancedb` | **memory-lancedb-pro** |\n|---------|--------------------------|----------------------|\n| Vector search | ✅ | ✅ |\n| BM25 full-text search | ❌ | ✅ |\n| Hybrid fusion (Vector + BM25) | ❌ | ✅ |\n| Cross-encoder rerank (Jina / custom endpoint) | ❌ | ✅ |\n--\n| `package.json` | NPM package info. Depends on `@lancedb/lancedb`, `openai`, `@sinclair/typebox` |\n| `cli.ts` | CLI commands: `memory list/search/stats/delete/delete-bulk/export/import/reembed/migrate` |\n| `src/store.ts` | LanceDB storage layer. Table creation / FTS indexing / Vector search / BM25 search / CRUD / bulk delete / stats |\n| `src/embedder.ts` | Embedding abstraction. Compatible with any OpenAI-API provider (OpenAI, Gemini, Jina, Ollama, etc.). Supports task-aware embedding (`taskQuery`/`taskPassage`) |\n| `src/retriever.ts` | Hybrid retrieval engine. Vector + BM25 → RRF fusion → rerank → recency / importance / length / decay weighting → noise filter → coarse MMR diversity. |\n| `src/recall-engine.ts` | Shared recall helpers: prompt gating, session repeated-injection suppression, tagged-block assembly, max-age filtering, and recent-per-key capping |\n| `src/auto-recall-final-selection.ts` | Generic auto-recall adapter. Maps `RetrievalResult` rows into final-selection candidates and applies generic `mmr | setwise-v2` behavior at the final cutoff seam |\n| `src/final-topk-setwise-selection.ts` | Shared final top-k selector. Owns shortlist presort, deterministic set-wise selection, lexical-overlap suppression, and optional embedding-based semantic redundancy suppression |\n--\n| `src/migrate.ts` | Migration tool. Migrates data from the built-in `memory-lancedb` plugin to Pro |\n\n---\n\n## Core Features\n\n### 1. Hybrid Retrieval\n\n```\nQuery → embedQuery() ─┐\n--\n- **Vector Search**: Semantic similarity via LanceDB ANN (cosine distance)\n- **BM25 Full-Text Search**: Exact keyword matching via LanceDB FTS index\n- **Fusion Strategy**: Vector score as base, BM25 hits get a 15% boost (tuned beyond traditional RRF)\n- **Configurable Weights**: `vectorWeight`, `bm25Weight`, `minScore`\n\n### 2. Cross-Encoder Reranking\n\n--\n- **Hybrid Scoring**: 60% cross-encoder score + 40% original fused score\n- **Graceful Degradation**: Falls back to cosine similarity reranking on API failure\n\n### 3. Multi-Stage Scoring Pipeline\n\n| Stage | Formula | Effect |\n--\n- CJK-aware thresholds (Chinese: 6 chars vs English: 15 chars)\n\n### 6. Noise Filtering\n\nFilters out low-quality content at both auto-capture and tool-store stages:\n- Agent refusal responses (\"I don't have any information\")\n--\n- `memoryReflection.enabled`: turn reflection features on/off\n- `memoryReflection.injectMode`:\n  - `inheritance-only` = inject inherited rules only\n  - `inheritance+derived` = inherited rules + derived-focus note on `/new` / `/reset`\n- `memoryReflection.recall.mode`:\n  - `fixed` = compatibility path\n--\n- `memoryReflection.storeToLanceDB`: store reflection event/item rows in LanceDB\n- `memoryReflection.agentId` (optional): use a dedicated reflection agent\n\nRecommended starter config:\n\n```json\n--\n    \"storeToLanceDB\": true,","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778036054866}}
{"type":"message","id":"f28b9965","parentId":"0f24000f","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:54:22.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the pro version. Let me also check the latest version and release notes.","thinkingSignature":"1a00dac6d8df4364addd2bfdc3b5af6bb27f00aea465f0c64952e940357da403"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rqrh38fmafcz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://api.github.com/repos/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/releases/latest\" 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('Latest:', d.get('tag_name'))\nprint('Date:', d.get('published_at'))\nprint('Body:', d.get('body','')[:500])\n\"","timeout":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rqrh38fmafcz_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://api.github.com/repos/openclaw/openclaw/contents/plugins/memory-lancedb\" 2>/dev/null | python3 -c \"\nimport sys,json; d=json.load(sys.stdin)\nprint('OpenClaw official memory-lancedb:')\nfor f in d:\n    print(f'  {f[\\\"name\\\"]}')\n\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38571,"output":247,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60885,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778036054871,"responseId":"0649e0579ab817d57d0a83e3b5160299"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2aa0551d","parentId":"f28b9965","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:54:22.812Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rqrh38fmafcz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Latest: v1.1.0-beta.10\nDate: 2026-03-23T18:53:30Z\nBody: ## What's Changed\n\n### Hook Migration (Breaking for OpenClaw < 2026.3.22)\n- Migrated `before_agent_start` hooks to `before_prompt_build` with explicit priority ordering (auto-recall=10, invariants=12, derived=15)\n- Eliminates \"Legacy before_agent_start\" deprecation warnings in OpenClaw 2026.3+\n\n### Bug Fixes\n- **Auto-recall gating**: Fixed regression where `shouldSkipRetrieval` short-message check never triggered (event.prompt contains full system prompt in `before_prompt_build`). Added `message"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":660,"aggregated":"Latest: v1.1.0-beta.10\nDate: 2026-03-23T18:53:30Z\nBody: ## What's Changed\n\n### Hook Migration (Breaking for OpenClaw < 2026.3.22)\n- Migrated `before_agent_start` hooks to `before_prompt_build` with explicit priority ordering (auto-recall=10, invariants=12, derived=15)\n- Eliminates \"Legacy before_agent_start\" deprecation warnings in OpenClaw 2026.3+\n\n### Bug Fixes\n- **Auto-recall gating**: Fixed regression where `shouldSkipRetrieval` short-message check never triggered (event.prompt contains full system prompt in `before_prompt_build`). Added `message","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778036062812}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca390e6c","parentId":"2aa0551d","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:54:22.812Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rqrh38fmafcz_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw official memory-lancedb:\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":755,"aggregated":"OpenClaw official memory-lancedb:\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778036062812}}
{"type":"message","id":"b850ed20","parentId":"ca390e6c","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:54:37.868Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough information to give a comprehensive comparison between the pro version and the original.","thinkingSignature":"8b9c68c520c32b8f5a52c54bdd36ab144951ac021eb2b6a4274a005c9d0836d6"},{"type":"text","text":"**4.3k star，MIT License，分支版比原版强不少。**\n\n---\n\n## 原版 vs Pro 版对比\n\n| 功能 | 原版 `memory-lancedb` | **Pro 版** |\n|------|---------------------|-----------|\n| 向量检索 | ✅ | ✅ |\n| BM25 全文搜索 | ❌ | ✅ |\n| **混合检索**（向量 + BM25 融合） | ❌ | ✅ |\n| **Cross-Encoder 重排**（Jina / OpenAI） | ❌ | ✅ |\n| 多作用域隔离（Agent/User/Project） | ❌ | ✅ |\n| 生命周期衰减 | ❌ | ✅ |\n| 记忆反思（Memory Reflection） | ❌ | ✅ |\n| 噪声过滤 | ❌ | ✅ |\n| MCP CLI 管理工具 | ❌ | ✅ |\n| 从原版迁移工具 | ❌ | ✅ |\n| 多语言 Embedding | 有限 | ✅（Jina、OpenAI、Ollama、Gemini 等）|\n| CJK 中文优化 | ❌ | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## 核心升级点\n\n**1. 混合检索**：不是纯向量匹配，而是向量 + BM25 双路融合，关键词精准匹配和语义理解兼顾\n\n**2. Cross-Encoder 重排**：检索结果再用 Jina reranker 精排，TOPK 质量更高\n\n**3. 多作用域隔离**：一个数据库支持多个 Agent / 用户 / 项目，互不干扰，适合你们多 Agent 团队\n\n**4. 中文优化**：CJK 阈值自适应（中文 6 字 vs 英文 15 字符）\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 注意\n\n- **Pro 版是 MIT License**，商用没问题\n- 依赖 **Jina AI**（免费 reranker）或个人 OpenAI API\n- 最新版已适配 **OpenClaw 2026.3+** 的 `before_prompt_build` hooks\n- 装好后一条命令可从原版迁移数据：`memory migrate`\n\n---\n\n**推荐你们用 Pro 版**，直接装这个而不是原版。要我帮你写安装配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39004,"output":454,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61525,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778036062816,"responseId":"0649e05f77f199d986e0624567e96770"}}
