{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b509eac6a00b4c351defcbc01ea3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-06 10:57 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"5ea56146","parentId":"13aa99d3","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:57:49.173Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"1d4c98ad","parentId":"5ea56146","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:58:12.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if they can use their existing API keys for memory-lancedb-pro. Looking at the config, they currently use minimax as their LLM provider. But memory-lancedb-pro supports OpenAI API format for embedding and reranking.\n\nLet me check what keys they currently have:\n- From the openclaw.json, they use `minimax` provider with `minimax/MiniMax-M2.7` model\n- They have a minimax API key\n\nFor memory-lancedb-pro, they need:\n1. Embedding: Jina, OpenAI, Ollama, etc.\n2. Reranker: Jina, SiliconFlow, or none\n\n\n3. LLM: OpenAI or compatible\n\nSince minimax doesn't directly support OpenAI-compatible embedding endpoints, they'd need either Jina (free tier available), OpenAI, or Ollama for embeddings. For the reranker, Jina or SiliconFlow would work. Their existing minimax key won't work directly for these components unless minimax has a compatible embedding endpoint, which I should verify.\n\nThey could potentially use their minimax API for the Smart Extraction LLM if minimax is OpenAI-compatible, but the embedding and reranking would still need separate keys from Jina, SiliconFlow, or OpenAI.","thinkingSignature":"af48062375706ebc6f883cbb8f71fcb7170aeaf1f3cb23cba20240d84067a741"},{"type":"text","text":"minimax 的 embedding 接口和 OpenAI 不完全兼容，**embedding 和 reranker 这两块还是需要额外 key**。\n\n不过 Jina 有免费额度，够你们前期用：\n\n| 用途 | 建议用 | 免费额度 |\n|------|--------|---------|\n| **Embedding** | Jina `jina-embeddings-v5-text-small` | 每天有限，够用 |\n| **Reranker** | Jina `jina-reranker-v3` | 有免费 tier |\n| **Smart Extraction LLM** | 你们的 minimax（如果兼容 OpenAI 格式） | 已有的 |\n\n---\n\n**最小成本方案：**\n\n- **Embedding**：Jina（免费）→ 需要注册拿 key\n- **Reranker**：Jina（免费）→ 同上\n- **Smart Extraction LLM**：你们已有的 minimax（如果 minimax 有 OpenAI 兼容 endpoint）\n\n---\n\nminimax 的 API 是 `https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1`，走的是 Anthropic 格式，**不是 OpenAI 格式**。\n\n所以 Smart Extraction 这块，要么：\n1. **再申请一个 OpenAI key**（最小方案）\n2. **用 Ollama 本地跑 qwen3:8b**（零费用，但要有一台有显存的机器）\n\n你们倾向于哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":539,"cacheRead":61111,"cacheWrite":5342,"totalTokens":67149,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778036269174,"responseId":"0649e12d51ced838095da38766565593"}}
