{"type":"message","id":"d4ed510a","parentId":"7e695e25","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:59:46.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if minimax supports OpenAI API standard (for embedding), or they can apply for a Jina key. Let me check if minimax has an OpenAI-compatible embedding endpoint.\n\nFrom what I know, minimax does support some OpenAI-compatible endpoints. Let me check their documentation or API.\n\nActually, looking at their current config:\n```json\n\"baseUrl\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\",\n\"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n```\n\nThis is Anthropic messages API format, not OpenAI. But they might have a separate endpoint for embeddings.\n\nLet me search for this or try to figure it out. I should also note that Jina has a free tier that can be signed up for at jina.ai.\n\n\nThe user wants to know if minimax can handle OpenAI-compatible embedding and reranking, otherwise they can just sign up for Jina since it has a free tier available.","thinkingSignature":"20269b42a927f7dc318966e84163309e07f5f44dcafce67c1477f170e65d41a2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jrr2nv7w4pek_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --connect-timeout 5 \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/models\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $MINIMAX_API_KEY\" 2>/dev/null | head -50","timeout":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jrr2nv7w4pek_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --connect-timeout 5 \"https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/embeddings\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $MINIMAX_API_KEY\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"embeddings\",\"input\":\"hello\"}' 2>/dev/null | head -30","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":374,"cacheRead":66227,"cacheWrite":566,"totalTokens":67324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":177803637