{"type":"message","id":"92429fd3","parentId":"0bb070c6","timestamp":"2026-05-06T02:59:55.105Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need the API key. Let me check if it's available in the environment or config.\n\nActually, from the openclaw.json I read earlier, the minimax API key is:\n`apiKey: \"sk-cp-…s38c\"` - it's truncated in the config.\n\nBut I can't use the actual key for testing. Let me just tell the user what I found - minimax uses a different auth format for the API key, and let me check if they have a separate embeddings endpoint.\n\nActually, let me just check the minimax documentation online to see if they support OpenAI-compatible embeddings.","thinkingSignature":"bac26f8e4b0e27ca08dfc2672be644253e352a9df0b9d41cfa77a170afe1d45f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9d47dlsjxuzu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://docs.minimaxi.com\" --max-time 8 2>/dev/null | head -20 || echo \"无法访问\"","timeout":12}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45340,"output":188,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67595,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778036387365,"responseId":"0649e1a364da2d786eca180f5075ecc7"}}
