{"type":"message","id":"3a03dbfd","parentId":"12f2de7f","timestamp":"2026-05-06T03:00:14.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Can't access the docs. Let me try a different approach - check if there's a way to test with the actual key, or just answer based on what I know.\n\nActually, I should be honest - I can't verify the minimax embedding endpoint without a valid key. But based on common knowledge:\n\n1. Minimax generally supports OpenAI-compatible APIs for some endpoints\n2. But embedding might be a separate service\n\nThe user suggested they could apply for a Jina key. That's probably the cleanest solution. Let me tell them:\n\n1. I can't verify minimax's embedding endpoint without a key\n2. Jina has free tier - easiest path\n\n\n3. The most straightforward approach would be applying for that Jina account and setting it up with their key\n\nBut wait - the user actually has an OpenAI key available, not minimax. That's the detail I was missing. So Plan C with OpenAI embedding would work, though it's not free. The real choice comes down to whether they want to use their existing OpenAI key with Plan C, go with Jina for the free embedding tier, or find another path forward.","thinkingSignature":"904d9f8b5aacfbee2dd26577eeecd6e7fd3ae833e113f6557171c8a763d4bdf2"},{"type":"text","text":"我没权限用你的 minimax key 测试，你可以自己试一下：\n\n```bash\ncurl https://api.minimaxi.com/v1/embeddings \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer 你的***\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"model\":\"embedding-model\",\"input\":\"hello\"}'\n```\n\n**如果返回 embedding 数据** → minimax 可以当 embedding 用，直接走 Plan C（OpenAI key 够用）。\n\n**如果报错** → 用 Jina 申请一个免费 key：\n👉 https://jina.ai/api-key\n\n---\n\n## 最终方案建议\n\n| 方案 | Embedding | Reranker | Smart Extraction | 费用 |\n|------|-----------|---------|-----------------|------|\n| **C（推荐）** | OpenAI `text-embedding-3-small` | 无 | 你们的 minimax | 你们的 OpenAI key 已够 |\n| **A（全功能）** | Jina（免费 key） | Jina | 你们的 minimax | 几乎免费 |\n\n你们已有 OpenAI key 的话，**Plan C 最快**，装完就能用，reranker 后面再加也行。要现在装吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45546,"output":478,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68091,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778036395264,"responseId":"0649e1ab7229fce8f0acd89091468986"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3bd0ca8e","parentId":"3a03dbfd","timestamp":"2026-05-06T03:01:25.522Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b509ebee43c88c2b4b8494a560a0]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: Embedding\n是不是特别费token"}],"timestamp":1778036485434}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b509ebee43c88c2b4b8494a560a0\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-06 11:01 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"785f247d","parentId":"3bd0ca8e","timestamp":"2026-05-06T03:01:25.536Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"9b0e11a4","parentId":"785f247d","timestamp":"2026-05-06T03:01:42.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether embedding consumes a lot of tokens. Let me give a quick, accurate answer about embedding token costs.","thinkingSignature":"580caf13bc0924a9269139fe5ddf8f54c5e7c09745721bb0ebd94599bbd44c2c"},{"type":"text","text":"还好，主要看**存多少内容**，不是查多少次。\n\n---\n\n## Embedding 消耗逻辑\n\n| 阶段 | 消耗 |\n|------|------|\n| **存储时**（memory_store） | 每次存储做一次 embedding，取决于内容长度 |\n| **查询时**（memory_recall） | 每次查询做一次 embedding，query 很短，token 很少 |\n\n---\n\n## 实际消耗估算\n\n假设你们每天：\n- **存储 50 条记忆**，每条平均 200 tokens\n- **查询 100 次**，每次 query 50 tokens\n\n```\n每天 embedding 消耗 ≈ 50 × 200 + 100 × 50 = 10,000 + 5,000 = 15,000 tokens\n每月 ≈ 450,000 tokens\n```\n\nOpenAI `text-embedding-3-small` 的价格：**$0.02 / 1M tokens**\n\n```\n每月 ≈ $0.009，几乎可以忽略不计\n```\n\n---\n\n## 真正费 token 的地方\n\n**不是 embedding，是 Smart Extraction（LLM 提炼记忆）**\n\n这个每条记忆都要调一次 LLM，消耗的是你们 minimax 的额度。\n\n---\n\n**总结：embedding 本身不贵，真正的消耗是 LLM 那部分。** Plan C（不用 reranker）已经是最省钱的方案了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":299,"cacheRead":66568,"cacheWrite":869,"totalTokens":67893,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778036485536,"responseId":"0649e207dad63289f56b19f34c66b49e"}}
