{"type":"message","id":"d5c98303","parentId":"efe54a4c","timestamp":"2026-05-06T03:04:19.500Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the image clearly. It shows the minimax OpenAI-compatible API page with various models and their prices. The user is pointing to the **text-embedding-3-small** model at **$0.02 / 1M tokens**.\n\nThis is the OpenAI embedding model, and it confirms that:\n1. The user has access to OpenAI API (since this page shows OpenAI's pricing)\n2. text-embedding-3-small is indeed $0.02 / 1M tokens\n3. The user wants to use this\n\nSo Plan C (text-embedding-3-small) is perfect - they can use their existing OpenAI API key for embedding. No need for Jina.\n\n\nThe user is essentially confirming they want to go with Plan C using text-embedding-3-small since they already have OpenAI API access.","thinkingSignature":"efd034d0ee99c0bc3e75322fff34a5b2e6311af476b9170d0cc9801d0891168a"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了，用 **text-embedding-3-small**，就是 Plan C 的方案。\n\n价格 **$0.02 / 1M tokens**，你们已有 OpenAI key 直接用就行。\n\n---\n\n## 确认 Plan C 配置\n\n```json\n{\n  \"embedding\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"***\",\n    \"model\": \"text-embedding-3-small\",\n    \"baseURL\": \"https://api.openai.com/v1\"\n  },\n  \"autoCapture\": true,\n  \"autoRecall\": true,\n  \"captureAssistant\": false,\n  \"smartExtraction\": true,\n  \"extractMinMessages\": 2,\n  \"extractMaxChars\": 8000,\n  \"llm\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"***\",\n    \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n    \"baseURL\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\"\n  },\n  \"retrieval\": {\n    \"mode\": \"hybrid\",\n    \"vectorWeight\": 0.7,\n    \"bm25Weight\": 0.3,\n    \"filterNoise\": true,\n    \"minScore\": 0.3,\n    \"hardMinScore\": 0.35\n  },\n  \"sessionMemory\": { \"enabled\": false }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n**要我现在开始装吗？**\n\n步骤：\n1. `openclaw plugins install memory-lancedb-pro@beta`\n2. 写入配置\n3. 重启验证"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":46624,"output":485,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69176,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778036645804,"responseId":"0649e2a6527308d517027f697f362b35"}}
