{"type":"message","id":"d49dbdb5","parentId":"0ed46d32","timestamp":"2026-05-06T03:04:50.618Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The image tool seems to be having issues. The user's image might not be accessible. But based on context - the user sent an image after I mentioned the text-embedding-3-small pricing at $0.02/1M tokens. The user is likely asking if this pricing is \"enough\" for their use case, or they might be showing me some pricing data from an OpenAI dashboard or similar.\n\nActually wait - they said \"够用吗\" which means \"Is it enough?\" - they might be asking if the free tier / their current plan is enough for their needs.\n\nBut I can't see the image. Let me try another approach.","thinkingSignature":"189c1b51bcb0e39dd3a9d3894e199f8d14355a387dbdd2987bbc799bbe221068"},{"type":"text","text":"图片我这边读不到，你发的是 OpenAI 的 embedding 用量截图吗？\n\n不管是什么，**Plan C 完全够用**：\n\n- `text-embedding-3-small` 0.02刀/1M tokens\n- 每月 45 万 tokens ≈ **不到 1 块钱人民币**\n- reranker 加上去也就多一个 Jina 免费额度\n\n你看到的是什么——是想确认免费额度够不够，还是想加 reranker？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":47375,"output":227,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69669,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778036680344,"responseId":"0649e2c8b5d06e113400663b24edbe88"}}
