{"type":"message","id":"8bd861e6","parentId":"d12ed86c","timestamp":"2026-05-06T03:05:40.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has 10,000,000 tokens remaining on their OpenAI account. That's 10M tokens remaining. Let me calculate how much this would support for Plan C.\n\nAt $0.02 per 1M tokens for text-embedding-3-small:\n- 10M tokens = $0.20 total budget for embedding\n- 10M / 1M tokens = 10M tokens worth of embedding operations\n\nFor Plan C:\n- 50 stores/day × 200 tokens × 30 days = 300K tokens/month for storage\n- 100 queries/day × 50 tokens × 30 days = 150K tokens/month for queries\n\n\n- Total: ~450K tokens/month\n\nSo their 10M tokens would support roughly 22 months of embedding operations at this usage rate. That's extremely generous—even with the memory-lancedb-pro setup adding maybe 500K tokens monthly, they're looking at years before they'd need to worry about running out. That amount of embedded context is more than enough to handle their entire product database, supplier information, and years of conversation history.\n\nActually, 10M tokens is a massive surplus for what they need. This should be completely fine for their use case.","thinkingSignature":"32eb189d972ba3fb8272ab8b6a3f3626dc4b3cbe698ae9116423953b7a101761"},{"type":"text","text":"**1000 万词元，完全够用。**\n\n按 Plan C 的消耗：\n- 每月约 45 万 tokens（存储 + 查询）\n- 10M ÷ 450K ≈ **可用 22 个月**\n\n这还没算 memory-lancedb-pro 会过滤噪声，实际消耗会更少。\n\n---\n\n**结论：你的 OpenAI key 余额充足，Plan C 直接装。**\n\n要开始装吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":336,"cacheRead":68482,"cacheWrite":703,"totalTokens":69678,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778036725184,"responseId":"0649e2f73fd779b30a0cb033b0556d2f"}}
