{"type":"message","id":"dcc85227","parentId":"f8c4aba8","timestamp":"2026-05-06T03:05:55.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the free tier/quota for text-embedding-3-small. They want to know if the free tier is enough. From the image, they have 10,000,000 tokens remaining - this is likely a free trial quota from OpenAI.\n\nThe question \"免费额度\" means \"is the free quota/tier enough?\" - they're asking if the free $5 or free trial credits OpenAI provides are sufficient for their use case.\n\nGiven that Plan C uses text-embedding-3-small at $0.02/1M tokens, and they have 10M tokens (which at $0.02/1M = $0.20), so with a typical $5 free trial they'd get 250M tokens, which would last them years.\n\n\nWith 10M tokens available, that's roughly 500 times what they'd consume monthly, so the free trial quota alone would sustain them for an extremely long time.","thinkingSignature":"d4cf5c8cbe4c00356663155369086b21fa37a5ab648a5f67690f8ca538e37b6f"},{"type":"text","text":"**免费额度完全够用。**\n\n10M tokens，按 Plan C 消耗速率：\n- 每月 ~45 万 tokens\n- **10M ÷ 450K ≈ 22 个月**\n\nOpenAI 免费 trial 额度对他们来说绑绑够，你们甚至不用考虑付费。\n\n---\n\n**开始装？**\n\n```bash\nopenclaw plugins install memory-lancedb-pro@beta\n```\n\n装完我来帮你写配置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":279,"cacheRead":68959,"cacheWrite":360,"totalTokens":69755,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778036744051,"responseId":"0649e3080f1fae9bd28bbe00ce2e7e57"}}
