{"type":"message","id":"fa6d9bc1","parentId":"fab0ede8","timestamp":"2026-05-06T03:09:14.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, npm install succeeded. Now I need to configure the plugin in openclaw.json. Based on the SKILL.md:\n\nFor git clone with workspace path, I need:\n```json\n{\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"load\": { \"paths\": [\"plugins/memory-lancedb-pro\"] },\n    \"allow\": [\"memory-lancedb-pro\"],\n    \"slots\": { \"memory\": \"memory-lancedb-pro\" },\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"memory-lancedb-pro\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          // Plan A config with Jina + minimax\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nI need to be careful to MERGE with existing config, not replace it. Let me read the current config first.\n\nActually, let me use the gateway tool to patch the config rather than editing the file directly.\n\nPlan A config:\n```json\n{\n  \"embedding\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"jina_4…8EU0\",\n    \"model\": \"jina-embeddings-v5-text-small\",\n    \"baseURL\": \"https://api.jina.ai/v1\",\n    \"dimensions\": 1024,\n    \"taskQuery\": \"retrieval.query\",\n    \"taskPassage\": \"retrieval.passage\",\n    \"normalized\": true\n  },\n  \"autoCapture\": true,\n  \"autoRecall\": true,\n  \"captureAssistant\": false,\n  \"smartExtraction\": true,\n  \"extractMinMessages\": 2,\n  \"extractMaxChars\": 8000,\n  \"llm\": {\n    \"apiKey\": \"***\",\n    \"model\": \"gpt-4o-mini\",\n    \"baseURL\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\"\n  },\n  \"retrieval\": {\n    \"mode\": \"hybrid\",\n    \"vectorWeight\": 0.7,\n    \"bm25Weight\": 0.3,\n    \"rerank\": \"cross-encoder\",\n    \"rerankProvider\": \"jina\",\n    \"rerankModel\": \"jina-reranker-v3\",\n    \"rerankEndpoint\": \"https://api.jina.ai/v1/rerank\",\n    \"rerankApiKey\": \"jina_4097b8316ad64d9586733e301731d266hCVyCvZ69_DHCHlPDjFHB8Gi8EU0\",\n    \"rerankModel\": \"jina-reranker-v3-base\",\n    \"candidatePoolSize\": 12,\n    \"minScore\": 0.6,\n    \"hardMinScore\": 0.62,\n    \"filterNoise\": true\n  },\n  \"sessionMemory\": { \"enabled\": false }\n}\n```\n\nThis is Plan A with Jina for both embedding and reranking, using minimax for the LLM component. Let me patch the config with this setup.","thinkingSignature":"90c97011d69f3f86cdc4abc8a683c49f872a68acc1f008b6e75e4866638026dd"},{"type":"text","text":"依赖装好。现在写入配置：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wxv7a9mpm32h_1","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.patch","path":"plugins","raw":"{\n  \"load\": {\n    \"paths\": [\"plugins/memory-lancedb-pro\"]\n  },\n  \"allow\": [\"memory-lancedb-pro\"],\n  \"slots\": {\n    \"memory\": \"memory-lancedb-pro\"\n  },\n  \"entries\": {\n    \"memory-lancedb-pro\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"config\": {\n        \"embedding\": {\n          \"apiKey\": \"jina_4097b8316ad64d9586733e301731d266hCVyCvZ69_DHCHlPDjFHB8Gi8EU0\",\n          \"model\": \"jina-embeddings-v5-text-small\",\n          \"baseURL\": \"https://api.jina.ai/v1\",\n          \"dimensions\": 1024,\n          \"taskQuery\": \"retrieval.query\",\n          \"taskPassage\": \"retrieval.passage\",\n          \"normalized\": true\n        },\n        \"autoCapture\": true,\n        \"autoRecall\": true,\n        \"captureAssistant\": false,\n        \"smartExtraction\": true,\n        \"extractMinMessages\": 2,\n        \"extractMaxChars\": 8000,\n        \"llm\": {\n          \"apiKey\": \"sk-cp-…s38c\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"baseURL\": \"https://api.minimaxi.com/anthropic/v1\"\n        },\n        \"retrieval\": {\n          \"mode\": \"hybrid\",\n          \"vectorWeight\": 0.7,\n          \"bm25Weight\": 0.3,\n          \"rerank\": \"cross-encoder\",\n          \"rerankProvider\": \"jina\",\n          \"rerankModel\": \"jina-reranker-v3\",\n          \"rerankEndpoint\": \"https://api.jina.ai/v1/rerank\",\n          \"rerankApiKey\": \"jina_4097b8316ad64d9586733e301731d266hCVyCv