{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5084966e4e00b21d0be1ffc62f3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-06 17:44 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"0fc4fc19","parentId":"5e9af2f5","timestamp":"2026-05-06T09:44:50.944Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"796ef4e0","parentId":"0fc4fc19","timestamp":"2026-05-06T09:45:04.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if Jina API requires a VPN/proxy to access. This is a fair question given the sandbox environment can't reach it.\n\nJina AI's API endpoint is `https://api.jina.ai`. In mainland China, this would likely require VPN access since it's a US-based service. The user's sandbox environment in this cloud infrastructure can't reach it either.\n\nLet me think about alternatives:\n1. Use a Chinese embedding service (like minimax, volcengine, etc.) instead of Jina\n2. Set up a proxy/VPN\n3. Use a Chinese embedding provider that doesn't require VPN\n\nFor a cross-border team, the Jina situation might indeed require VPN access in China.\n\n\nI should outline some practical workarounds they could pursue.","thinkingSignature":"bff6fd6c38fd9a013d1effa77ad44bff8a62ef5dea985660b7a399d2f83ecb73"},{"type":"text","text":"是的，**Jina 是境外服务**（`api.jina.ai`），在国内访问需要翻墙。\n\n你们有几条路：\n\n---\n\n## 方案 1：继续用 Jina + 翻墙\n\n适合你们跨境团队，海外节点访问 Jina 完全没问题。\n\n## 方案 2：换用国内 Embedding 服务\n\n| 服务 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| **minimax embedding** | 国内直连，已有 key |\n| **SiliconFlow** | 国内可用，部分模型免费 |\n| **dashscope（阿里）** | 国内直连 |\n| **volcengine（豆包）** | 国内直连，便宜 |\n\n## 方案 3：Ollama 本地部署\n\n完全离线，无需翻墙，embedding 模型本地跑。\n\n---\n\n## 我的建议\n\n你们跨境团队**很可能本身就需要翻墙**（做海外业务）。如果是这样，**Jina 直接用就行**，不用换。\n\n如果不想折腾——**换 minimax embedding** 最简单，你们已有 key，国内直连。\n\n换哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":374,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":80187,"totalTokens":80718,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778060690945,"responseId":"064a409366ba11b43af35b51f2ad6fb7"}}
