model\": \"jina-embeddings-v5-text-small\",\n      \"dimension\": 1024\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n--\nAvailable Jina models:","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778060830452}}
