{"type":"message","id":"55d15ac0","parentId":"32493dc5","timestamp":"2026-05-06T09:48:36.360Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The configuration looks good. Now I need to summarize the situation for the user. The files are ready, but they need to deploy this on a server that has internet access (to reach Jina API and MiniMax API).\n\nImportant note: The user asked about using MiniMax for VLM in OpenViking. From the docs I found earlier, the supported VLM providers in OpenViking include: volcengine, openai, openai-codex, kimi, and glm. I need to confirm whether minimax is supported as a VLM provider. I didn't get a clear confirmation from the docs. Let me tell the user what I've configured and note the uncertainty.\n\nActually, looking at the docs again:\nFor VLM: \"volcengine\" (Doubao), \"openai\", \"openai-codex\", \"kimi\", \"glm\"\n\nI don't see \"minimax\" in the VLM providers list. \n\nBut I did see \"minimax\" in the embedding providers list. So the minimax VLM might not be supported yet—the docs clearly show the VLM options are volcengine, openai-codex, kimi, and glm. I should be upfront with the user that MiniMax may not work as a VLM in OpenViking and suggest they consider volcengine's Doubao as an alternative Chinese VLM provider instead.","thinkingSignature":"9be3d0e492339d4319446397e284f35bec5e7acabdc66da16a6e6f14b535922b"},{"type":"text","text":"**配置已准备好，但有个问题需要确认：**\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ VLM 配置注意事项\n\nOpenViking 的 VLM provider 支持这些：\n- `volcengine`（豆包，推荐国内使用）\n- `openai` \n- `openai-codex`\n- `kimi`\n- `glm`\n\n**`minimax` 是否支持 VLM** 我没在文档里找到确认。如果你那边启动报错，换成 `volcengine`（豆包）就行，国内直连。\n\n---\n\n## 部署步骤（在有网络的服务器上跑）\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.openviking\ndocker-compose up -d\n\n# 验证\ncurl http://localhost:1933/health\n\n# 查看日志\ndocker logs openviking\n```\n\n---\n\n## 现状总结\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 配置文件 | ✅ 已写好 |\n| Docker compose | ✅ 已写好 |\n| 部署 | ⏳ 你在服务器上跑一下 |\n| Jina embedding | ✅ 共用同一个 key |\n| MiniMax VLM | ⚠️ 待验证，不行换 volcengine |\n\n你先跑一下，有问题发给我。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64811,"output":520,"cacheRead":21794,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87125,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778060902406,"responseId":"064a41677393e338f25575f0378b38aa"}}
