{"type":"message","id":"619ff2d6","parentId":"2e054daa","timestamp":"2026-05-06T09:51:01.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether the Jina free tier API quota is sufficient for their use case. I don't actually know the specific Jina free tier limits - I should be honest about this and tell them to check their Jina dashboard for current usage/limits. I don't have access to their Jina account to check the quotas.","thinkingSignature":"97270fb4bda546b56d1ad85476ec4d8e2789a39c8ea062bb1cadd632b59f4196"},{"type":"text","text":"Jina 免费 tier 的具体额度我不太清楚，建议你自己查一下：\n\n👉 **https://jina.ai/api-key** （登录后看 Dashboard）\n\n免费版有**速率限制**（RPM/TPM），不是无限额度。\n\n**你们 5-6 个 Agent 的消耗估算：**\n- 每次查询 ≈ 几十 tokens\n- 每天几百次查询 ≈ 几万 tokens\n\n按这个量级**大概率够用**，但如果并发高、记忆量大，可能触发限流。\n\n建议先看 Dashboard 里你的免费额度是多少，再判断够不够。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":185,"cacheRead":85817,"cacheWrite":510,"totalTokens":86669,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778061055022,"responseId":"064a41fff229073bc34d7979e2a1025b"}}
