{"type":"message","id":"a2a6bce2","parentId":"840f45a7","timestamp":"2026-05-06T12:47:27.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the SKILL.md to understand what it does.","thinkingSignature":"8eace231a2cbbe04e6391a0f146c8a95dea3e2059ce1c545005c6a7602798f7f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e7d9lpzcgw5q_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/capability-evolver/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":66399,"output":77,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88543,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778071644077,"responseId":"064a6b5cde2eda7c8c10a17919a44f04"}}
{"type":"message","id":"115a4d60","parentId":"a2a6bce2","timestamp":"2026-05-06T12:47:27.834Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e7d9lpzcgw5q_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: capability-evolver\ndescription: Local evolution engine for OpenClaw (offline, no EvoMap)\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\": {\"always\": true}}\n---\n\n# Capability Evolver (OpenClaw Integration)\n\n## How it works\n- Automatically review session logs when OpenClaw session ends\n- Self-heal tool call errors and optimize execution logic\n- Background \"dream learning\" when OpenClaw is idle\n- 100% offline, no network connection to EvoMap\n\n## Usage\nRun manually when you want to evolve prompts:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver && node index.js\n```\n\nOr use as part of OpenClaw skill system.\n\n## Configuration\nSet evolution strategy via environment variable:\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced` (default, recommend)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=innovate` (max innovation)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=harden` (enhance security)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=repair-only` (only fix errors)\n\n## Offline Mode\nEvolver runs completely offline without any network connection to EvoMap Hub.\nNo `.env` file is needed - this is the default behavior when A2A_HUB_URL is not set."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":26,"aggregated":"---\nname: capability-evolver\ndescription: Local evolution engine for OpenClaw (offline, no EvoMap)\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\": {\"always\": true}}\n---\n\n# Capability Evolver (OpenClaw Integration)\n\n## How it works\n- Automatically review session logs when OpenClaw session ends\n- Self-heal tool call errors and optimize execution logic\n- Background \"dream learning\" when OpenClaw is idle\n- 100% offline, no network connection to EvoMap\n\n## Usage\nRun manually when you want to evolve prompts:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver && node index.js\n```\n\nOr use as part of OpenClaw skill system.\n\n## Configuration\nSet evolution strategy via environment variable:\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced` (default, recommend)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=innovate` (max innovation)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=harden` (enhance security)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=repair-only` (only fix errors)\n\n## Offline Mode\nEvolver runs completely offline without any network connection to EvoMap Hub.\nNo `.env` file is needed - this is the default behavior when A2A_HUB_URL is not set.","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778071647834}}
