{"type":"message","id":"2111d911","parentId":"12a0e76b","timestamp":"2026-05-06T12:47:57.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So capability-evolver is not actually configured as a skill. It's just sitting in the workspace directory. It hasn't been running at all.\n\nLet me give the user an honest assessment.","thinkingSignature":"4a2b636ad66edc250361e5140843c551ab254c8089db7a35b48c262eb547c289"},{"type":"text","text":"**没有，数据说话：**\n\n```\n日志搜索 \"capability-evolver\" → 0 条记录\nskill 配置 → 未注册\n```\n\n---\n\n## capability-evolver 现状\n\n它**躺在 workspace 里，没有被启用**，原因：\n\n1. **不在 `skills.entries` 里** → OpenClaw 不知道要加载它\n2. **metadata 说 `always: true`** 但这只是声明，不等于自动生效\n3. **需要手动配置** 才能跑\n\n---\n\n## 它实际做什么\n\n根据 SKILL.md：\n- 每次会话结束后自动 review 日志\n- 自我修复工具调用错误\n- 空闲时后台\"梦境学习\"\n- 完全离线，不连外部服务\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\n**它对我没有产生任何作用**，因为没有配置启用。\n\n要启用它吗？还是说先确认清楚这个项目值不值得装？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67429,"output":214,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89710,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778071668882,"responseId":"064a6b75a0b6ff776c8c6fc0b7051abd"}}
