{"type":"message","id":"c4015c26","parentId":"c91016cf","timestamp":"2026-05-06T12:51:55.780Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zjz7hffp2k6k_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"code\": 99991672,\n  \"msg\": \"Access denied. One of the following scopes is required: [drive:drive, drive:drive:readonly, drive:file:readonly, drive:file, drive:file:download].应用尚未开通所需的应用身份权限：[drive:drive, drive:drive:readonly, drive:file:readonly, drive:file, drive:file:download]，点击链接申请并开通任一权限即可：https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93650c6fc785bce/auth?q=drive:drive,drive:drive:readonly,drive:file:readonly,drive:file,drive:file:download&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant\",\n  \"error\": {\n    \"log_id\": \"202605062051527757424F75CC47420F94\",\n    \"troubleshooter\": \"排查建议查看(Troubleshooting suggestions): https://open.feishu.cn/search?from=openapi&log_id=202605062051527757424F75CC47420F94&code=99991672&method_id=6944991842538733569\",\n    \"permission_violations\": [\n      {\n        \"subject\": \"drive:drive\",\n        \"type\": \"action_scope_required\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"type\": \"action_scope_required\",\n        \"subject\": \"drive:drive:readonly\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"type\": \"action_scope_required\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":65,"aggregated":"{\n  \"code\": 99991672,\n  \"msg\": \"Access denied. One of the following scopes is required: [drive:drive, drive:drive:readonly, drive:file:readonly, drive:file, drive:file:download].应用尚未开通所需的应用身份权限：[drive:drive, drive:drive:readonly, drive:file:readonly, drive:file, drive:file:download]，点击链接申请并开通任一权限即可：https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93650c6fc785bce/auth?q=drive:drive,drive:drive:readonly,drive:file:readonly,drive:file,drive:file:download&op_from=openapi&token_type=tenant\",\n  \"error\": {\n    \"log_id\": \"202605062051527757424F75CC47420F94\",\n    \"troubleshooter\": \"排查建议查看(Troubleshooting suggestions): https://open.feishu.cn/search?from=openapi&log_id=202605062051527757424F75CC47420F94&code=99991672&method_id=6944991842538733569\",\n    \"permission_violations\": [\n      {\n        \"subject\": \"drive:drive\",\n        \"type\": \"action_scope_required\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"type\": \"action_scope_required\",\n        \"subject\": \"drive:drive:readonly\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"type\": \"action_scope_required\"","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778071915780}}
{"type":"message","id":"7fa4ef82","parentId":"c4015c26","timestamp":"2026-05-06T12:52:04.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The app doesn't have drive permissions to download files. The Feishu app lacks the `drive:file:download` scope. \n\nHowever, the user sent this file as an attachment to the chat message. The file_key is for the Feishu message attachment system, not the drive system. In Feishu, message attachments use a different API - the IM message file API.Let me try the IM API for message files.\n\nActually, looking at the Feishu API docs, for message attachments (not drive files), the endpoint would be something like:\n`GET /im/v1/messages/{message_id}/resources/{file_key}`\n\nBut I don't have the message_id. The file_key itself is `file_v3_0111e_45552b13-77db-4292-b08a-e0cc660d72ag`.\n\nThe app doesn't have the drive permission scope, and that's needed to download files from Feishu. I should let the user know that the app lacks the necessary permissions.","thinkingSignature":"5110431e3b9790c336583dde357d6475ada449aca2d6a67dcb1c4e5518f2f913"},{"type":"text","text":"**文件下载失败**，原因是飞书应用没有 `drive:file:download` 权限。\n\n需要你在飞书开放平台给应用开通这个权限：\n\n👉 https://open.feishu.cn/app/cli_a93650c6fc785bce/auth\n\n添加权限：`drive:file` 或 `drive:file:readonly`\n\n开通后我才能读到这个文件。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":72562,"output":289,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94918,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778071915789,"responseId":"064a6c6c3608d21080d6de92b72cec3c"}}
