{"type":"message","id":"7d1bf5f9","parentId":"98a29674","timestamp":"2026-05-06T12:56:12.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still failing. The `file_key` format `file_v3_0111e_...` suggests it's a drive file. But maybe the `cli_a93650c6fc785bce` app's permission issue is different - maybe the app needs to be re-installed by the tenant admin, or there's a token type issue.\n\nLet me try getting a user access token instead, since the file might be shared with the user but not the app.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The user is saying the SKILL.md file is available via Feishu. But maybe instead of trying to download it, I should just look at what capability-evolver already has in the workspace and read its SKILL.md locally, since the user said to install \"这个skill\".\n\n\nWait, I'm overcomplicating this. The capability-evolver is already cloned in the workspace. The user probably just wants me to enable it as a skill and activate it, not install it from Feishu. Let me re-read what they're actually asking for - they said \"发给你的是skill，安装这个skill，启动这个项目\". So the Feishu file might just be documentation or additional context, and what they really want is to set up what's already in the workspace.\n\nLet me look at the existing capability-evolver SKILL.md to see what needs to be done for setup.","thinkingSignature":"9a1f60a2b74add00d20c2bd7db20fdae5238ba1fcbc5718d42ee6fee1847cd30"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v5elwmel7rrs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/capability-evolver/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":75256,"output":338,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778072163619,"responseId":"064a6d63f23a0d06c2c61c6731a326c7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"32fa7433","parentId":"7d1bf5f9","timestamp":"2026-05-06T12:56:12.654Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_v5elwmel7rrs_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: capability-evolver\ndescription: Local evolution engine for OpenClaw (offline, no EvoMap)\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\": {\"always\": true}}\n---\n\n# Capability Evolver (OpenClaw Integration)\n\n## How it works\n- Automatically review session logs when OpenClaw session ends\n- Self-heal tool call errors and optimize execution logic\n- Background \"dream learning\" when OpenClaw is idle\n- 100% offline, no network connection to EvoMap\n\n## Usage\nRun manually when you want to evolve prompts:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver && node index.js\n```\n\nOr use as part of OpenClaw skill system.\n\n## Configuration\nSet evolution strategy via environment variable:\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced` (default, recommend)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=innovate` (max innovation)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=harden` (enhance security)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=repair-only` (only fix errors)\n\n## Offline Mode\nEvolver runs completely offline without any network connection to EvoMap Hub.\nNo `.env` file is needed - this is the default behavior when A2A_HUB_URL is not set."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":33,"aggregated":"---\nname: capability-evolver\ndescription: Local evolution engine for OpenClaw (offline, no EvoMap)\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\": {\"always\": true}}\n---\n\n# Capability Evolver (OpenClaw Integration)\n\n## How it works\n- Automatically review session logs when OpenClaw session ends\n- Self-heal tool call errors and optimize execution logic\n- Background \"dream learning\" when OpenClaw is idle\n- 100% offline, no network connection to EvoMap\n\n## Usage\nRun manually when you want to evolve prompts:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/skills/capability-evolver && node index.js\n```\n\nOr use as part of OpenClaw skill system.\n\n## Configuration\nSet evolution strategy via environment variable:\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced` (default, recommend)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=innovate` (max innovation)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=harden` (enhance security)\n- `EVOLVE_STRATEGY=repair-only` (only fix errors)\n\n## Offline Mode\nEvolver runs completely offline without any network connection to EvoMap Hub.\nNo `.env` file is needed - this is the default behavior when A2A_HUB_URL is not set.","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778072172654}}
