{"type":"message","id":"5cb4853c","parentId":"06731c1e","timestamp":"2026-05-06T12:58:23.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's running! The evolver is scanning session logs and producing evolution output. This is actually working. The key output shows it's analyzing session logs and generating mutations based on the GEP (Genome Evolution Protocol).\n\nLet me now summarize the results for the user.","thinkingSignature":"22e30a01d77787e7edb420768947b4cc907c3e8f47870ee55bf61836aaacd164"},{"type":"text","text":"**跑起来了，有数据产出。**\n\n```\nStarting evolver...\nScanning session logs...\nGEP — GENOME EVOLUTION PROTOCOL (v1.10.3 STRICT) Cycle #0001\n\n检测到的信号:\n- score-only: user_feature_request, tool_bypass\n- Multi-strategy: regex=3, score=2, llm=0, merged=5\n```\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\n**capability-evolver 已安装并正常工作。**\n\n它做的事情：\n1. 扫描你的 OpenClaw 会话日志\n2. 分析工具调用错误、绕过、用户请求等信号\n3. 按 GEP 协议生成进化方案（Mutation、PersonalityState、EvolutionEvent 等 JSON 对象）\n4. 离线运行，不走外部 API\n\n---\n\n**对你有没有用？**\n\n取决于你想不想让 AI 自我演进优化。如果你希望 AI 每次犯错后自动学习和改进，它有用。如果只是需要一个稳定的助手，现有的 memory-core + dreaming 可能更实用。\n\n要继续深入用它，还是先停在这里？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80907,"output":267,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778072293882,"responseId":"064a6de6ad98939af12f67f80178e6ef"}}
