{"type":"message","id":"d5120c59","parentId":"d91a6c7f","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:00:55.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether capability-evolver and memory-core + dreaming are conflicting or overlapping. Let me clarify the distinction.\n\n- memory-core + dreaming: stores and organizes memories, recalls past context\n- capability-evolver: analyzes session logs, finds tool call errors, generates mutation proposals to improve the AI's behavior/skills\n\nThey are NOT the same:\n- memory-core = memory storage and retrieval (what happened, what was decided)\n- capability-evolver = self-improvement engine (why things failed, how to get better)\n\nThey are complementary, not conflicting. They serve different purposes.","thinkingSignature":"bb1338860c177a72d2550087056cbf900156561da961b208643dc4209b3fc446"},{"type":"text","text":"**不冲突，是互补的。**\n\n简单说：\n\n| | 负责什么 |\n|---|---------|\n| **memory-core + dreaming** | 记住东西（对话、决策、上下文） |\n| **capability-evolver** | 改进能力（分析错误、优化工具调用逻辑） |\n\n---\n\n- **memory-core** = 记忆仓库\n- **capability-evolver** = 质检员 + 训练师\n\n两者各管各的，可以同时开着。现在已经是 ✅ ready 状态，不用管它，它会在后台自动运行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":231,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":79188,"totalTokens":101643,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778072443304,"responseId":"064a6e7b5304938a09be6b415f4ac0bd"}}
