{"type":"message","id":"62b9b426","parentId":"ef696526","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:03:53.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have real data to show. Let me summarize what I found.","thinkingSignature":"c8a1763da95e5be4a06209557766c421e991998f823a9b8ce48760d8d2cd2070"},{"type":"text","text":"**有数据，它确实跑过了。**\n\n---\n\n## 它分析出了什么\n\n**检测到的信号（从你的会话日志）：**\n```\nrepeated_tool_usage:exec    — 反复用 exec 工具\nuser_feature_request       — 用户请求新功能\ntool_bypass               — 绕过了某些工具\n```\n\n**它生成的性格配置：**\n```json\n{\n  \"rigor\": 0.7,          // 严谨度 70%\n  \"creativity\": 0.35,    // 创造力 35%\n  \"verbosity\": 0.25,     // 输出简洁\n  \"risk_tolerance\": 0.4, // 风险偏好适中\n  \"obedience\": 0.85      // 服从性 85%\n}\n```\n\n**选择的进化方向：** `innovate`（创新），选了 `gene_gep_innovate_from_opportunity` 基因\n\n---\n\n## 数据文件\n\n| 文件 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `evolution_solidify_state.json` | 本次进化状态 |\n| `memory_graph.jsonl` | 分析的信号记录 |\n| `personality_state.json` | 当前性格配置 |\n| `memory_graph_state.json` | 演进历史状态 |\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\n**它有用。** 它从你实际的会话里分析出工具使用模式，生成了性格参数和进化建议。数据存在 `memory/evolution/` 目录下。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":82624,"output":314,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105005,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778072622124,"responseId":"064a6f2eb5a7ab0849390a40bbf539b0"}}
