{"type":"message","id":"99af546a","parentId":"d37ec38f","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:05:20.816Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The memory directory is only 48K, which is tiny. The key files are:- `evolution/` directory - contains evolution state, memory graph, personality state\n- `evolver_update_check.json` - update check stateThese are the files that contain all the learned evolution data. The user can just copy this directory to the new environment.","thinkingSignature":"432cfc2de72151d04fa34f3b72d3bd2b08ed080b15a46b9a6839219ae5c560b2"},{"type":"text","text":"**能。数据很小，才 48K。**\n\n迁移时只需要拷这三个东西：\n\n```\ncapability-evolver/\n├── memory/\n│   ├── evolution/              ← 进化状态、记忆图谱\n│   │   ├── evolution_solidify_state.json\n│   │   ├── memory_graph.jsonl\n│   │   ├── memory_graph_state.json\n│   │   └── personality_state.json\n│   └── evolver_update_check.json\n├── SKILL.md\n└── index.js\n```\n\n---\n\n**迁移步骤：**\n1. 把整个 `skills/capability-evolver/` 目录拷到新环境的 `workspace/skills/`\n2. `npm install` 重装依赖\n3. 重启 Gateway\n\n**不需要重新训练**，性格参数、记忆图谱、进化历史都在 `memory/` 里，拷走就能无缝衔接。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":83141,"output":248,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105456,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778072712062,"responseId":"064a6f885f8161dc6b482b6abc3425e4"}}
