{"type":"message","id":"671ae24f","parentId":"0d2d4bcd","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:06:24.605Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! There's a `backup.sh` and an `evolver.sh`. Let me check the backup.sh to see what's being backed up.","thinkingSignature":"32aca6cee8c0ed6ad939348e588f2ce3d14f30c9b3c8c1acb56447b6f346ad12"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_35lbw52roc3k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/backup.sh","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":84801,"output":83,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778072781404,"responseId":"064a6fcd16fe3eb32d362883f2263beb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"acc48b47","parentId":"671ae24f","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:06:24.674Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_35lbw52roc3k_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Daily Backup Script (v3.1 — 2026-04-21)\n# 只做备份，不跑 evolver\n\nBACKUP_REPO=\"/tmp/openclaw-backup-clone\"\nOPENCLAW_DIR=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nGIT_REF=\"main\"\nDATE_DIR=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\n\nGH_TOKEN=*** \"oauth_token:\" ~/.config/gh/hosts.yml | awk '{print $2}')\n\necho \"[$(date)] Starting OpenClaw backup...\"\n\n# Clone or update backup repo\nif [ -d \"$BACKUP_REPO/.git\" ]; then\n  cd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\n  git checkout \"$GIT_REF\" 2>/dev/null\n  git pull origin \"$GIT_REF\" --quiet\nelse\n  rm -rf \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\n  git clone \"https://${GH_TOKEN}@github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git\" \"$BACKUP_REPO\" --quiet\nfi\n\n# Fresh date dir (replace old snapshot entirely)\nrm -rf \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR\"\nmkdir -p \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR\"\n\n# rsync helper: dest always inside $DATE_DIR/\ndo_rsync() {\n  local src=\"$1\"\n  local dst=\"$2\"   # relative to $DATE_DIR/\n  if [ -e \"$src\" ]; then\n    rsync -a --exclude='.git' \"$src\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/$dst\"\n  fi\n}\n\n# 1. Core config files (no trailing slash = copy as file)\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json\" \"\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json.bak\" \"\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json.bak.1\" \"\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openviking.env\" \"\"\n\n# 2. Directories (trailing slash = copy contents)\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/agents/\" \"agents/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/credentials/\" \"credentials/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/cron/\" \"cron/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/devices/\" \"devices/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/flows/\" \"flows/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/identity/\" \"identity/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/feishu/\" \"feishu/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/subagents/\" \"subagents/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/extensions/\" \"extensions/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/skills/\" \"skills/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"workspace/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-main/\" \"workspace-main/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/memory/\" \"memory/\"\ndo_rsync \"$HOME/.evomap/\" \"evomap/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/qqbot/\" \"qqbot/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw-weixin/\" \"openclaw-weixin/\"\n\n# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nif [ -n \"$(git status --porcelain)\" ]; then\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\n\n  # ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\n  SCRIPT_DIR=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\" && pwd)\"\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"✅ 每日备份完成\\n📦 备份 → 已推送至 openclaw-backup\" && echo \"[$(date)] Backup Feishu notification sent\" || echo \"[$(date)] Failed to send Feishu notification\"\n  # ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nfi"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":21,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Daily Backup Script (v3.1 — 2026-04-21)\n# 只做备份，不跑 evolver\n\nBACKUP_REPO=\"/tmp/openclaw-backup-clone\"\nOPENCLAW_DIR=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nGIT_REF=\"main\"\nDATE_DIR=$(date '+%Y-%m-%d')\n\nGH_TOKEN=$(grep \"oauth_token:\" ~/.config/gh/hosts.yml | awk '{print $2}')\n\necho \"[$(date)] Starting OpenClaw backup...\"\n\n# Clone or update backup repo\nif [ -d \"$BACKUP_REPO/.git\" ]; then\n  cd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\n  git checkout \"$GIT_REF\" 2>/dev/null\n  git pull origin \"$GIT_REF\" --quiet\nelse\n  rm -rf \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\n  git clone \"https://${GH_TOKEN}@github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git\" \"$BACKUP_REPO\" --quiet\nfi\n\n# Fresh date dir (replace old snapshot entirely)\nrm -rf \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR\"\nmkdir -p \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR\"\n\n# rsync helper: dest always inside $DATE_DIR/\ndo_rsync() {\n  local src=\"$1\"\n  local dst=\"$2\"   # relative to $DATE_DIR/\n  if [ -e \"$src\" ]; then\n    rsync -a --exclude='.git' \"$src\" \"$BACKUP_REPO/$DATE_DIR/$dst\"\n  fi\n}\n\n# 1. Core config files (no trailing slash = copy as file)\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json\" \"\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json.bak\" \"\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw.json.bak.1\" \"\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openviking.env\" \"\"\n\n# 2. Directories (trailing slash = copy contents)\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/agents/\" \"agents/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/credentials/\" \"credentials/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/cron/\" \"cron/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/devices/\" \"devices/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/flows/\" \"flows/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/identity/\" \"identity/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/feishu/\" \"feishu/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/subagents/\" \"subagents/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/extensions/\" \"extensions/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/skills/\" \"skills/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"workspace/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace-main/\" \"workspace-main/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/memory/\" \"memory/\"\ndo_rsync \"$HOME/.evomap/\" \"evomap/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/qqbot/\" \"qqbot/\"\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/openclaw-weixin/\" \"openclaw-weixin/\"\n\n# Commit and push\ncd \"$BACKUP_REPO\"\nif [ -n \"$(git status --porcelain)\" ]; then\n  git config user.email \"backup@openclaw\"\n  git config user.name \"OpenClaw Backup\"\n  git add -A\n  git commit -m \"Full backup $DATE_DIR $(date '+%H:%M')\"\n  git push origin \"$GIT_REF\"\n  echo \"[$(date)] Backup pushed to GitHub\"\n\n  # ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\n  SCRIPT_DIR=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\" && pwd)\"\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"✅ 每日备份完成\\n📦 备份 → 已推送至 openclaw-backup\" && echo \"[$(date)] Backup Feishu notification sent\" || echo \"[$(date)] Failed to send Feishu notification\"\n  # ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date)] No changes, skipping commit\"\nfi","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778072784674}}
{"type":"message","id":"1d5d4ef6","parentId":"acc48b47","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:06:31.877Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the backup script. It backs up `skills/` which would include `capability-evolver`. But the key question is whether the `memory/` directory of capability-evolver is being backed up.Looking at the script:- `do_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"workspace/\"` - this would back up the entire workspace directory, which includes `workspace/skills/capability-evolver/` including its `memory/` subdirectory.So yes, the capability-evolver data IS included in the backup through `workspace/`.But wait, there's also a separate `evolver.sh` - let me check what that does.","thinkingSignature":"a714c65cd9abe52a6325ac819e92f6453edd2be432baa13dbbb4d0621aa8487d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kp6wg18vgi6y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/openclaw-backup/evolver.sh","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":85765,"output":186,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108018,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778072784681,"responseId":"064a6fd1850dfc231a205be81cb9d7d3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"62580051","parentId":"1d5d4ef6","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:06:31.956Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kp6wg18vgi6y_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Capability Evolver Standalone Runner\n# 独立运行 evolver，单独发飞书通知\n\nLOG_FILE=\"/tmp/openclaw-evolver.log\"\nEVOLVER_DIR=\"/home/halei/skills/capability-evolver\"\n\necho \"[$(date)] Starting Capability Evolver...\"\n\n{\n  cd \"$EVOLVER_DIR\"\n  EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced node index.js run 2>&1\n  EVOLVE_EXIT=$?\n} > >(tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\")\n\necho \"[$(date)] Capability evolver finished with exit $EVOLVE_EXIT\"\n\n# ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\nSCRIPT_DIR=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\" && pwd)\"\nif [ $EVOLVE_EXIT -eq 0 ]; then\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"🧬 Capability Evolver 完成（exit 0）\" && echo \"[$(date)] Evolver Feishu notification sent\"\nelse\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"⚠️ Capability Evolver 有错误（exit $EVOLVE_EXIT）\" && echo \"[$(date)] Evolver Feishu notification sent\"\nfi\n# ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":32,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n# Capability Evolver Standalone Runner\n# 独立运行 evolver，单独发飞书通知\n\nLOG_FILE=\"/tmp/openclaw-evolver.log\"\nEVOLVER_DIR=\"/home/halei/skills/capability-evolver\"\n\necho \"[$(date)] Starting Capability Evolver...\"\n\n{\n  cd \"$EVOLVER_DIR\"\n  EVOLVE_STRATEGY=balanced node index.js run 2>&1\n  EVOLVE_EXIT=$?\n} > >(tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\")\n\necho \"[$(date)] Capability evolver finished with exit $EVOLVE_EXIT\"\n\n# ── Send Feishu notification ──────────────────────────────────────\nSCRIPT_DIR=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\" && pwd)\"\nif [ $EVOLVE_EXIT -eq 0 ]; then\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"🧬 Capability Evolver 完成（exit 0）\" && echo \"[$(date)] Evolver Feishu notification sent\"\nelse\n  node \"$SCRIPT_DIR/send-to-me.js\" \"⚠️ Capability Evolver 有错误（exit $EVOLVE_EXIT）\" && echo \"[$(date)] Evolver Feishu notification sent\"\nfi\n# ── End Feishu notification ────────────────────────────────────────","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778072791956}}
{"type":"message","id":"74283d27","parentId":"62580051","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:06:39.762Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can now give a clear answer. The backup script (`backup.sh`) does include `workspace/` which contains `capability-evolver/memory/`. So yes, the evolver's data IS being backed up.","thinkingSignature":"789db79ee8a82867b5b93e07d3099a17c1ca78dcc9674431d0887925d0f4ba5c"},{"type":"text","text":"**是的，已经包含了。**\n\n看 `backup.sh` 第 45 行：\n```bash\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/\" \"workspace/\"\n```\n\n整个 `workspace/` 都被备份，里面有：\n```\nworkspace/skills/capability-evolver/memory/evolution/  ← 进化数据\n```\n\n---\n\n## 另外还有一个 `evolver.sh`\n\n这是**单独跑 evolver** 的脚本，有独立的飞书通知。\n\n两个配合：\n- `backup.sh` → 备份所有数据（包括 evolver 的 memory）\n- `evolver.sh` → 单独触发 evolver 跑一次进化\n\n---\n\n## 结论\n\n**capability-evolver 的数据在每日备份里**，不用担心丢失。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":86233,"output":193,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778072791962,"responseId":"064a6fd839bb7cff260071db66da92b9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a72ae37","parentId":"74283d27","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:08:21.954Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b50879afaa0a0c3bd714b40d1757]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 好的， 我有一个架构问题咨询你， 我现在正在搭建一个跨境电商团队，选品，运营，等。 如果我在组织一个自媒体团队。 你是建议都在你的这个openclaw下进行，还是其它系统里面单独组建？"}],"timestamp":1778072901860}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50879afaa0a0c3bd714b40d1757\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-06 21:08 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"41485648","parentId":"2a72ae37","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:08:21.973Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"32002a09","parentId":"41485648","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:08:52.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a big architecture question about whether to run multiple teams (cross-border e-commerce team + self-media team) all within OpenClaw, or to build them in separate systems.\n\nThis is a strategic decision that requires understanding the trade-offs. Let me think about this carefully:\n\n**OpenClaw as a central AI orchestration hub:**\n- Multi-agent architecture already in place (main + tts agents)\n- Shared memory, skills, tools\n- Feishu integration already set up\n- Centralized management\n\n**Arguments for keeping everything in OpenClaw:**\n1. Single pane of glass - one system to manage\n2. Shared knowledge base - decisions, context, memory all shared\n3. Lower cost - no duplicate infrastructure\n4. Cross-functional collaboration - e.g., a product discovered by the selection team can be used by content team\n\n\n5. Centralized access control and auditability\n\n**Arguments for separating teams:**\n1. Data isolation - different teams shouldn't see each other's data\n2. Performance - more agents might slow things down\n3. Complexity - one big system is harder to manage\n4. Ownership - clearer who owns what\n5. Scaling - can scale each team independently\n\nThe real answer depends on whether the teams need to collaborate. If the e-commerce team sources products and the self-media team creates content about them, keeping them together under OpenClaw makes sense. But if they're completely independent with no overlap, separation might be cleaner.\n\nThe practical recommendation is to run both teams through OpenClaw's multi-agent system but give each its own agent identity and scoped memory access. This way they share infrastructure while maintaining data separation. That said, OpenClaw isn't built to replace project management tools like Notion or Feishu for task management and collaboration—it's more of an orchestration and automation layer that works alongside existing systems rather than replacing them.","thinkingSignature":"04af98bfdfdf19eda47ec035995541d110f0f0e26836da21d6a85ae3da2eba13"},{"type":"text","text":"这是个很好的架构问题。让我先问你几个关键问题再给建议：\n\n---\n\n## 核心问题\n\n1. **两个团队之间有没有业务交集？**\n   - 选品团队选出来的产品，自媒体团队要用吗？\n   - 如果是上下游关系 → OpenClaw 统一管理有优势\n\n2. **两套团队用同一套飞书账号体系吗？**\n   - 如果是 → OpenClaw 可以承接所有 AI 助手\n   - 如果自媒体团队用其他 IM → 单独考虑\n\n3. **你对 AI 管理的需求是：**\n   - A）每个员工都有一个 AI 助手（偏向协作工具）\n   - B）团队共享几个 AI Agent 处理业务流程（偏向自动化）\n\n---\n\n## 我的初步倾向\n\n**如果两个团队业务有协同（选品→内容→运营），强烈建议都放在 OpenClaw 下。**\n\n好处是：\n- 共享产品知识库（选品发现的爆品 → 内容团队直接用）\n- 共享 SOP 和决策记忆\n- 一套基础设施，成本低\n\n**如果自媒体团队是纯内容生产，和电商没太多交集**，可以考虑独立。\n\n---\n\n## OpenClaw 能承载的团队规模\n\n当前你们：\n- 1 个 main Agent\n- 1 个 tts Agent（选品）\n\n扩展到多团队后的架构大概是这样：\n```\nOpenClaw（一个 Gateway）\n├── 跨境电商 Team\n│   ├── 选品 Agent\n│   ├── 运营 Agent\n│   └── 供应链 Agent\n├── 自媒体 Team\n│   ├── 内容 Agent\n│   └── 投放 Agent\n└── 共享知识库（OpenViking/LanceDB）\n```\n\n每个 Agent 有独立 workspace + 团队共享知识库。\n\n---\n\n## 关键风险提示\n\n| 风险 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **权限隔离** | OpenClaw 目前是单租户，多团队要靠 Agent 之间的访问控制 |\n| **并发性能** | Agent 多了会吃内存和 token 预算 |\n| **飞书机器人** | 每个团队可能需要不同的飞书应用来区分 |\n\n---\n\n**你的具体场景是什么？** 告诉我两个团队的协作关系，我帮你定架构。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":831,"cacheRead":105022,"cacheWrite":3016,"totalTokens":109026,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778072901973,"responseId":"064a70463a3d008173d608c9cf08b37b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dceafc4a","parentId":"32002a09","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:10:55.256Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b50879300b8a4c1044582a4188ba]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 趁着现在agent还在搭建中，是不是现在就分好目录？"}],"timestamp":1778073055163}}
