{"type":"message","id":"e5cf3574","parentId":"7bc36aeb","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:11:04.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether they should set up the directory structure now while agents are still being built. This is a great point - thinking ahead about the multi-team architecture and setting up proper workspace directories before things get too complex.\n\nLet me think about what directory structure would make sense for their cross-border e-commerce + self-media team setup. I should look at the current workspace structure and propose an organized layout.\n\nKey considerations:\n1. Each team (e-commerce, self-media) should have its own workspace\n2. Shared resources should be accessible to both\n3. Knowledge base should be organized by team and shared\n4. Agent configurations should be clear\n\nLet me look at the current workspace and propose a structure.","thinkingSignature":"c05eea7014fd0393983e5f70711049820df64ed084de1f43c9a06a98a2ba9c49"},{"type":"text","text":"说得对，趁早规划。来看一下现状：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q8ub9i71h0na_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/\necho \"---\"\nls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/agents/ 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\nls -la /home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector/ 2>/dev/null","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":157,"output":251,"cacheRead":107812,"cacheWrite":741,"totalTokens":108961,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778073055274,"responseId":"064a70df66c4eb9b1cd4a37c2879dd2a"}}
