{"type":"message","id":"29ce8efc","parentId":"43f49184","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:11:25.345Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the current structure:\n- `/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/` - has `main` and `tts` agents\n- `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/` - main workspace\n- `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/Selector/` - tts agent's workspace\n- `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-main/` - seems to be an older copy\n- `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace-selector/` - seems to be an older copy\n\nThe current structure is:\n```\nworkspace/\n├── main/ (or in root)\n├── Selector/\n├── agents/\n│   ├── main/\n│   └── tts/\n├── skills/\n├── memory/\n├── openviking/\n└── plugins/\n```\n\nFor a multi-team setup, I should propose:\n\n```\nworkspace/\n├── shared/                    # 共享目录\n│   ├── knowledge-base/        # 共享知识库\n│   ├── SOP/                  # 标准操作流程\n│   ├── products/             # 产品资料库\n│   └── team/\n├── e-commerce/               # 跨境电商团队\n│   ├── products/             # 产品相关\n│   ├── sourcing/             # 供应链/选品\n│   ├── operations/           # 运营\n│   └── supply-chain/         # 供应链\n├── social-media/             # 自媒体团队\n│   ├── content/              # 内容创作\n│   ├── channels/             # 平台管理\n│   └── creative/\n└── agents/\n    ├── main/                 # 大管家\n    ├── tts/                  # 选品大师\n    ├── content/              # 内容 Agent\n    ├── operations/           # 运营 Agent\n    └── social/               # 自媒体 Agent\n\nOrganizing the workspace this way makes sense since agents will need to reference shared resources across teams while maintaining team-specific directories.","thinkingSignature":"69c2e35ebc2ba91c1562ff8fbd163fe6cad3dee9477b86ab1ca4d0ad836e4a03"},{"type":"text","text":"\n对，现在目录比较乱，趁早规划好。\n\n**建议目录结构：**\n\n```\nworkspace/\n├── shared/                          # 共享资源（所有 Agent 都能读）\n│   ├── knowledge-base/              # 共享知识库（SOP、合规文档）\n│   ├── products/                    # 产品资料库（选品结果、爆品记录）\n│   ├── team/                        # 团队信息（人员、角色、权限）\n│   └── docs/                        # 共享文档\n│\n├── e-commerce/                     # 跨境电商团队\n│   ├── sourcing/                    # 选品相关\n│   ├── operations/                  # 运营相关\n│   └── supply-chain/                # 供应链\n│\n├── social-media/                    # 自媒体团队\n│   ├── content/                     # 内容创作\n│   ├── creative/                    # 创意素材\n│   └── channels/                    # 平台管理\n│\n└── agents/                          # Agent 配置\n    ├── main/                        # 大管家\n    ├── tts/                         # 选品大师\n    ├── content/                     # 内容 Agent（新建）\n    ├── operations/                  # 运营 Agent（新建）\n    └── social/                      # 自媒体 Agent（新建）\n```\n\n---\n\n**现在要整理吗？** 我可以：\n1. 把现有的 `Selector/` 里的内容迁移到 `e-commerce/sourcing/`\n2. 新建 `social-media/` 目录结构\n3. 建立 `shared/` 共享目录\n4. 更新 openclaw.json 里的 agent 配置\n\n你们团队现在有哪些 Agent 在用了？告诉我我来帮你规划。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":89752,"output":730,"cacheRead":22067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112549,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778073064698,"responseId":"064a70e97b1173ed58541d5950dc3cee"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d52058b","parentId":"29ce8efc","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:12:36.292Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b5087aad3e4a4c4c54be674258cc]\nou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: 你刚才不是建议这样弄个吗OpenClaw（一个 Gateway）\n├── 跨境电商 Team\n│ ├── 选品 Agent\n│ ├── 运营 Agent\n│ └── 供应链 Agent\n├── 自媒体 Team\n│ ├── 内容 Agent\n│ └── 投放 Agent\n└── 共享知识库（OpenViking/LanceDB）"}],"timestamp":1778073156194}}
