{"type":"message","id":"6f1d3ff6","parentId":"3dce78d5","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:12:53.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is confirming the architecture I suggested earlier. They want me to proceed with creating this structure in OpenClaw. Let me plan this out:\n\n1. Create the directory structure\n2. Configure agents in openclaw.json\n3. Set up the team structure\n\nCurrent state:\n- 2 agents: main, tts\n- Need to add: operations, supply-chain, content, social media投放\n\nLet me create the structure and configure the agents. I need to be careful about:\n1. Not disrupting existing work\n2. Properly configuring the bindings for routing\n3. Creating proper workspace directories\n\nLet me ask about the specific agents they want first, since the existing tts agent is for \"TK 选品大师\" which seems to be product selection. I need to understand if operations, supply-chain, content, and social agents need separate configurations.\n\nActually, the user confirmed the architecture. Let me proceed with creating the structure. I'll create:\n1. Directory structure under workspace/\n2. Agent configurations in openclaw.json\n3. Bindings for each agent\n\nBut I should first ask about the media agent since that's for the social media team, or confirm what each agent should do.\n\nWait - the user is asking me to just do it. Let me ask a quick clarifying question about what each new agent should do, or just proceed with the structure and placeholder configs.","thinkingSignature":"6cafa29629d5db2a8816371dbcf669e41078900064e2126b62adee280cb71765"},{"type":"text","text":"好，直接开干。先确认一下：\n\n你们现在有：\n- `main`（大管家）\n- `tts`（TK 选品大师）\n\n新增需要：\n- 运营 Agent\n- 供应链 Agent\n- 内容 Agent\n- 投放 Agent\n\n**每个新 Agent 的职责是什么？** 我需要知道他们各自负责什么，才能写好 SOUL.md 和配置。\n\n比如：\n- 运营 Agent → 管店铺运营数据、分析、广告投放？\n- 供应链 Agent → 管库存、物流、供应商？\n- 内容 Agent → 写短视频脚本、图文内容？\n- 投放 Agent → 负责 TK/IG 广告投放？\n\n告诉我每个 Agent 的核心职责，我一起把目录和配置全建好。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"mini